<template><div><h1 id="is-fullwidth-code-point" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#is-fullwidth-code-point" aria-hidden="true">#</a> is-fullwidth-code-point <a href="https://travis-ci.org/sindresorhus/is-fullwidth-code-point" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://travis-ci.org/sindresorhus/is-fullwidth-code-point.svg?branch=master" alt="Build Status"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a></h1>
